00:21:00,692 --> 00:21:02,205
zogt er,

359
00:21:02,363 --> 00:21:04,011
"blayb bay mir nekhtikn,

360
00:21:04,152 --> 00:21:07,605
un morgn in der fri vel ikh avekgeyn zen vos es tut zikh bay aykh."

361
00:21:07,797 --> 00:21:10,879
un oyf morgn in der fri iz er avek un er iz gekumen.

362
00:21:11,053 --> 00:21:15,704
zogt er, "me, me yogt alemen in geto. ikh bin," zogt er, "nit dergangen biz aykh.

363
00:21:16,504 --> 00:21:21,527
vos vestu ton? efsher blayb bay mir." zog ikh, "neyn. ikh vil tsu di mamen. vu di mame, dortn ikh.

364
00:21:21,533 --> 00:21:23,046
ikh gey oykh in geto."

365
00:21:23,963 --> 00:21:26,032
un agev dem gantsn lebn

366
00:21:26,646 --> 00:21:28,327
hot es im gematert,

367
00:21:28,620 --> 00:21:31,722
un dem gan- un oyf der elter, shoyn a mol lozn a trer,

368
00:21:31,722 --> 00:21:37,383
zogt er, "Mashe, ikh shpir zikh shuldik, vos ikh hob dir gelozn geyn in geto. kh'hob dir nit getort lozn geyn in geto.

369
00:21:37,383 --> 00:21:39,887
kh'volt dir bahaltn, khotsh untern bet, khotsh vu.

370
00:21:39,893 --> 00:21:43,633
kh'hob dir nit getort," zo- zogt er, "nor az du host genumen veynen, (az) du vilst tsu di mamen."

371
00:21:45,478 --> 00:21:52,964
un er hot mir bagleyt. er hot aroysgenumen fun t- in, fun portfel dortn... ikh hob (gere-) firt di, (ge)trogn mayne bikhlekh, tomer me vet mir farhaltn, az ikh gey tsum lerer...

372
00:21:53,578 --> 00:21:57,068
hot er aroysgenumen ale (di s-) heftn mit di bikher. zogt er, "dos darfst(u) shoyn nit."

373
00:21:57,068 --> 00:21:59,428
er hot arayngeleygt alts vos iz bay im geven:

374
00:21:59,637 --> 00:22:02,499
a bisele KONFITYUR, a shtikl broyt,

375
00:22:02,775 --> 00:22:05,435
a bisele, nit far yidn gedakht, khazer-fets,

376
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:07,168
dos vos er hot gehat.

377
00:22:07,168 --> 00:22:10,475
un er hot mir bagleyt bizn, biz dem ort vu m'hot gemakht,

378
00:22:10,475 --> 00:22:13,704
ir farshteyt, m'hot geyogt di yidn un glaykhtsaytik geboyt dem toyer.

379
00:22:16,326 --> 00:22:20,572
dos iz geven oyf Rudnitsker gas, RŪDNINKŲ in litvish, Rudnitsker gas.

380
00:22:21,034 --> 00:22:23,241
un ikh bin a gantsn tog arumgegangen

381
00:22:23,241 --> 00:22:24,453
un gefregt,

382
00:22:24,679 --> 00:22:26,883
tsi do i- fun hoyf tsu hoyf.

383
00:22:26,907 --> 00:22:29,629
mentshn zaynen gegangen mit di peklekh, mit di kinder,

384
00:22:29,629 --> 00:22:36,182
vayle m'hot gelozn nemen in geto nor dos vos men ke-, m'hot gegebn finf minut oyf zikh tsu f- greyt tsu zayn,

385
00:22:36,306 --> 00:22:40,181
un m'hot gelozn nemen nor dos, vos men ken trogn oyf zikh.

386
00:22:40,575 --> 00:22:45,102
iz gut vos di mame hot genumen a kindershe vanele vos me fleg bodn di kinder.

387
00:22:45,102 --> 00:22:46,500
zi hot dortn arayngeforn

388
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,923
zeyere vareme mantlen, vareme shikh,

389
00:22:48,923 --> 00:22:54,204
genumen a shtrik, zikh ayngeshpant vi a ferd un geshlept, vayl oyf di hent volt zi es nit gekent.

390
00:22:54,666 --> 00:22:56,972
un di shvester un di beyde kleyne.

391
00:22:58,041 --> 00:23:02,878
un zaynen avek, zey zaynen avek in geto. un ikh bin gegangen fun shtub, un mentshn,

392
00:23:03,188 --> 00:23:07,479
ir veyst, s'iz geven aza gefil az dos iz tsaytvaylik, az dos epes ken nit zayn.

393
00:23:07,479 --> 00:23:10,370
m'iz gezesn oyf di trep, m'iz gezesn in di tsimern,

394
00:23:10,495 --> 00:23:13,813
m- m'hot farnumen dires. un ikh bin gegangen fun shtub tsu shtub

395
00:23:13,937 --> 00:23:18,031
un gefregt, "s'iz do imetser fun Daytshe gas?" mir hobn damolst gelebt oyf Daytshe gas.

396
00:23:18,848 --> 00:23:23,111
un agev damolst ot azoy, d- s'iz geven dem zekstn september, eyn un fertsik,

397
00:23:23,522 --> 00:23:25,038
VOT azoy geyendik

398
00:23:25,038 --> 00:23:26,453
fun shtub tsu shtub,

399
00:23:26,847 --> 00:23:28,174
hob ikh geshafn

400
00:23:28,315 --> 00:23:29,186
a lid.

401
00:23:29,833 --> 00:23:31,059
tsu fertsn yor.

402
00:23:31,217 --> 00:23:33,354
dos iz der eyntsiker mol in lebn

403
00:23:33,816 --> 00:23:35,323
ven ikh hob farfast

404
00:23:35,323 --> 00:23:37,438
nit shraybndik, normal, vi...

405
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,649
 nu, ikh'l pruvn...

406
00:23:39,435 --> 00:23:41,083
ir gedenkt di verter?

407
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:45,290
ikh, ikh gedenk, ikh'l pruvn, ikh'l pruvn zikh dos dermonen, ikh, farshteyt zikh az ikh gedenk.

408
00:23:45,713 --> 00:23:49,453
dos iz a bisl, ikh bavunder biz itster, vayle tsu fertsn yor,

409
00:23:50,708 --> 00:23:53,233
dos iz a bisl mistike... ikh veys afile nit,

410
00:23:53,256 --> 00:23:57,604
 efsher psikhologn kenen dos derklern. ikh aleyn ken dos nit derklern.

411
00:23:59,476 --> 00:24:01,282
dos klingt umgefer azoy:

412
00:24:02,115 --> 00:24:03,782
"lakh, tayvl, lakh,

413
00:24:03,782 --> 00:24:07,622
in dayn tayvlshn gelaf, lakh zikh oys fun mentshn's laydn,

414
00:24:07,622 --> 00:24:09,737
loyf un kling mit dayne keytn.

415
00:24:09,861 --> 00:24:13,477
ven vest loyfn dayn galop, rays fun mir arop mayn kop,

416
00:24:13,477 --> 00:24:17,139
ganve bay a kind a shmeykhl, a toyt kerper fun a meydl,

417
00:24:17,139 --> 00:24:20,688
nem a mame's mid geveyn ven zi blaybt on kind aleyn,

418
00:24:20,695 --> 00:24:24,502
un s'varem hertsl fun dem kind nokh der shkhite vi a rind.

419
00:24:24,745 --> 00:24:28,688
nem a hant vos iz shoyn kalt, makh derfun a kleyn geshtalt.

420
00:24:28,845 --> 00:24:32,382
ven vest loyfn vi a vint, iber taykhn, berg geshvind,

421
00:24:32,389 --> 00:24:36,129
zolstu nemen dem geshtalt, eydes fun dem meysim-vald.

422
00:24:36,372 --> 00:24:43,284
loyfn zolst mit im tsuzamen iber felder, taykhn, yamen, un zolst alemen bavayzn, az payn shtarker iz fun ayzn.

423
00:24:43,341 --> 00:24:47,749
in dayn lakhn zol zikh hern vi es royshn yamim trern."

424
00:24:48,353 --> 00:24:49,967
dos iz tsu fertsn yor.

425
00:24:52,352 --> 00:24:54,949
di mamen hob ikh nit getrofn. m'hot gezogt az fun

426
00:24:54,949 --> 00:25:00,035
V- fun Vilner... dos iz a gantse epopee a bazundere. m'hot gezogt az fun Daytshe gas hot men geyogt in f-

427
00:25:00,035 --> 00:25:01,391
f- in tsveyte geto.

428
00:25:01,633 --> 00:25:06,656
un do tref ikh dem zelbn mit-shiler velkher hot mir n-, nit gelozn damolst arayn in gimnazye

429
00:25:06,848 --> 00:25:08,023
mit a biks.

430
00:25:08,687 --> 00:25:10,250
un ikh gey tsu tsu im.

431
00:25:10,712 --> 00:25:14,300
"(KAUKORAS)," zog ikh, "fir mir ariber in tsveyte geto.

432
00:25:14,543 --> 00:25:17,287
shis mir nit. fir mir ariber; dortn iz mayn mame."

433
00:25:18,070 --> 00:25:19,582
"gut," zogt er, "kum."

434
00:25:20,415 --> 00:25:23,289
un er hot mir... vayle on a biks hob ikh shoyn nit gekent geyn. s'iz shoyn geven,

435
00:25:23,289 --> 00:25:24,881
m'hot shoyn geboyt dem toyer.

436
00:25:25,512 --> 00:25:29,235
un m'hot geyogt in geto. vi k- m- fun geto hot men shoyn keynem nit aroysgelozn.

437
00:25:30,102 --> 00:25:32,098
hot er mir mitn biks gefirt

438
00:25:32,098 --> 00:25:33,760
un gebrakht in yene geto,

439
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:35,785
un dortn iz shoyn geven a gants hoykher toyer.

440
00:25:35,785 --> 00:25:38,128
zogt er, "shpringen!" zog ikh, "ikh'l shpringen."

441
00:25:38,168 --> 00:25:42,549
khotsh ikh shtel zikh nit for vi bin ikh aroyfgekrokhn, un bin aropgeshprungen oyf untn.

442
00:25:42,606 --> 00:25:47,578
un a, un g- un vider a gantsn d- a g- kumedikn tog... genekhtikt epes ergets in a kikh...

443
00:25:47,837 --> 00:25:49,994
un a gantsn tog gezukht

444
00:25:49,994 --> 00:25:50,986
di mamen.

445
00:25:51,415 --> 00:25:55,495
nor tsu mayn mazl, fun dortn hot men aroysgeho-, -gehoybn ale

446
00:25:55,495 --> 00:25:57,437
litvishe un poylishe

447
00:25:57,437 --> 00:25:59,529
aynvoyner. zey hot men gegebn

448
00:25:59,529 --> 00:26:01,416
mit di, di dires, di yidishe.

449
00:26:01,455 --> 00:26:03,086
hob ikh dortn getrofn

450
00:26:03,177 --> 00:26:07,544
undzere... zi iz geven, eyn tsayt iz zi geven bay undz,

451
00:26:07,544 --> 00:26:11,355
nu, zi hot gefirt di virtshaft, a hoyz-froy, a kekhin. zi flegt helfn mamen,

452
00:26:11,479 --> 00:26:12,992
fun dest vegn, fir kinder.

453
00:26:13,082 --> 00:26:14,986
(PRANĖ). zog ikh, "(PRANĖ),

454
00:26:14,986 --> 00:26:16,462
gey avek tsu undz

455
00:26:16,462 --> 00:26:19,016
in shtub un zog az ikh bin do in geto.

456
00:26:19,579 --> 00:26:21,412
ikh ken nit gefinen di mamen."

457
00:26:22,802 --> 00:26:26,373
iz, un (PRANĖ), zey hot men gegebn, di, di, di litviner hot men gegebn

458
00:26:26,633 --> 00:26:28,618
a ferd mit a vogn aroystsufirn.

459
00:26:28,658 --> 00:26:33,022
un zi iz geforn tsvey mol. meyle, nokh dem hob ikh zikh dervust az di mame iz fort in ershte geto.

460
00:26:33,805 --> 00:26:39,958
un d- un dan hot men glaykh geshafn a geto-politsey, un der (m- m-) shef fun geto-politsey iz gevorn GENSAS.

461
00:26:41,128 --> 00:26:45,285
un er hot b- b- bakumen... s'iz zeyer a, a figur zeyer a

462
00:26:45,285 --> 00:26:50,201
shver, mit eyn vort, un nit, un nit dos iz mayn tsil, tsu zikh funanderklaybn vos dos iz geven far a figur...

463
00:26:50,241 --> 00:26:55,702
nor er hot, b- di ershte teg hot er bakumen a (bal-), a derloybenish bay di daytshn,

464
00:26:55,759 --> 00:26:59,856
 az men zol, fareynikn di mishpokhes velkhe...

465
00:26:59,856 --> 00:27:03,991
er hot UNK gezogt az di ver es hobn kroyvim in ershte geto kenen zikh baytn.

466
00:27:03,991 --> 00:27:09,472
un m'hot undz oykh durkh biksn aribergefirt in di ershte geto, un dortn iz shoyn geven di mame mit di shvester.

467
00:27:09,495 --> 00:27:10,901
mir hobn zikh getrofn.

468
00:27:10,901 --> 00:27:12,763
un azoy hot zikh ongehoybn,

469
00:27:13,275 --> 00:27:14,619
 der lebn

470
00:27:14,659 --> 00:27:17,083
in geto. "lebn" ken men dos nit onrufn,

471
00:27:17,781 --> 00:27:19,327
nor der zayn in geto.

472
00:27:20,008 --> 00:27:25,672
di gantse historye fun geto iz shver ibertsukhazern, vi azoy s'iz gegangen di sim- sistematishe umkumen.

473
00:27:25,763 --> 00:27:30,813
fun onfang iz geven azoy: az m'vet, lozn lebn nor di velkhe arbetn.

474
00:27:31,112 --> 00:27:35,159
fun geto hot men aroysgelozn nor durkh a kleynem, a kleyne tirl. es iz geven

475
00:27:35,159 --> 00:27:35,691
a-,

476
00:27:35,691 --> 00:27:37,866
arum un arum zaynen geven hoykhe vent,

477
00:27:37,866 --> 00:27:42,463
nor eyne iz geven a toyer. der toyer flegt zikh efenen nor az me fleg darfn aroysforn un araynfirn.

478
00:27:42,621 --> 00:27:46,537
un azoy iz dos geven nor a, a kleyner, a kleyner toyer.

479
00:27:46,537 --> 00:27:52,352
fun yener zayt flegn shteyn dortn daytshn oder litviner fun di fabrikn, velkhe darfn yidishe arbets-kraft,

480
00:27:52,982 --> 00:27:55,518
un ale hobn zikh gerisn aroysgeyn oyf der arbet,

481
00:27:55,518 --> 00:27:57,650
kedey tsu krign dem AUSWEIS,

482
00:27:58,112 --> 00:28:02,476
vayle bay nakht a kontrol, ver es hot nit dem oysvayz, mit di mishpokhe firt men...

483
00:28:02,533 --> 00:28:04,884
di ershte tsayt hot men gezogt az me firt in,

484
00:28:04,884 --> 00:28:10,559
 in lit- litviner rufn dos PANERIAI, nor in yidish iz geven di alte poylishe Ponar,

485
00:28:10,937 --> 00:28:13,243
un ale lider zaynen alts in Ponar,

486
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:14,441
vegn Ponar.

487
00:28:14,532 --> 00:28:22,001
hot men gezogt az dortn iz an arbets-lager, ober g-, zeyer gikh hobn mir zikh dervust az dortn iz nito keyn arbets-lager, az dortn zaynen do griber, un me shist.

488
00:28:23,053 --> 00:28:25,100
di mame hot farshtanen,

489
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:27,384
oder imetser hot ir dos, untergezogt,

490
00:28:27,424 --> 00:28:32,663
zikh farshraybn az zi iz a shnayderke, vayle m'hot gedarft hobn nor arbeter, nor FACHARBEITER.

491
00:28:32,773 --> 00:28:36,682
hot men ir genumen, iz zi arayngefaln in a pal- pelts-fabrik, un zi hot gekrogn

492
00:28:37,077 --> 00:28:39,669
ot dem AUSWEIS, az zi arbet.

493
00:28:39,709 --> 00:28:44,017
iz bay nakht, az s'iz geven di kontrol, mir di fir kinder, azoy zaynen mir geblibn lebn.

494
00:28:44,017 --> 00:28:49,282
in a gevise tsayt arum hot men gezogt az me darf hobn nor, nor FACHARBEITER, gute, s'heyst di vos hobn

495
00:28:49,282 --> 00:28:52,910
stam geramt di, di gasn, oder d-... di darf men nit hobn.

496
00:28:52,910 --> 00:28:54,682
nor azoy vi di mame iz geven

497
00:28:54,682 --> 00:28:57,439
a shnayderke, zey hobn gen- dos iz in a pelts-fabrik,

498
00:28:57,681 --> 00:28:59,953
un di daytshn hobn gefrorn oyfn front,

499
00:29:00,111 --> 00:29:08,401
iz dortn iz geven nokh, hot men g- hot men gedarft zey s- d- di n- vikh- di, di, zeyer, zey, zaynen geven farinteresirt, zey zoln hobn di yidishe ar-, arbeter.

500
00:29:08,401 --> 00:29:10,753
hot zi gekrogn dem shtempele FACHARBEITER.

501
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:14,938
zaynen mir vider oyf a por monat ge- ge- geblibn lebn.

502
00:29:15,096 --> 00:29:16,729
nokh dem iz geven,

503
00:29:16,729 --> 00:29:19,743
 ikh hob do gebrakht andere fotografyes, nit ale,

504
00:29:19,743 --> 00:29:23,732
nor in shtub hob ikh. nit undzere. mayne hob ikh nit gefunen, ober nokhn krig hob ikh gefunen

505
00:29:23,732 --> 00:29:31,762
un ge- farshteyt zikh, mayn shtub iz nit YAD-VASHEM, nor a groysn, a groysn albom mit dokumentn, dermit vos ikh hob gekent

506
00:29:31,870 --> 00:29:33,866
oyfklaybn.

507
00:29:33,866 --> 00:29:36,341
"JUDE," di gele late. "OST,"

508
00:29:36,341 --> 00:29:39,271
OSTARBEITER, dos iz di nit-yidn vos m'hot aroysgefirt.

509
00:29:39,271 --> 00:29:42,815
 dem, a, a blekhele vos mir hobn getrogn. azelkhe zakhn hob ikh.

510
00:29:43,918 --> 00:29:49,177
un nokh dem hot men gezogt az me lozt nor gute FACHARBEITER, di gikh- gute FACHARBEITER veln krign

511
00:29:49,386 --> 00:29:54,392
dray, nor dray toyznt arbeter. dos iz umgefer a dritl fun ale aynvoyner fun g- fun ale arbeter.

512
00:29:54,745 --> 00:29:58,611
vider hot geholfn, got hot geholfn, az di mame hot gekrogn dem

513
00:29:58,971 --> 00:30:01,060
FACHARBEITERAUSWEIS, nor

514
00:30:01,060 --> 00:30:05,227
tsum FACHARBEITERAUSWEIS hot men gemegt hobn, dos heyst, tsushraybn, hot dos geheysn,

515
00:30:05,227 --> 00:30:07,802
a man oder a vayb un kinder biz zibetsn yor.

516
00:30:07,802 --> 00:30:10,558
di shvester hot (zi) farshribn mit a, yor yinger.

517
00:30:10,682 --> 00:30:13,615
a gantse nakht iz gegangen di registratsye un undz,

518
00:30:13,615 --> 00:30:14,847
dos heyst di

519
00:30:14,847 --> 00:30:18,231
mitglider fun der mishpokhe velkhe hobn rekht tsu lebn,

520
00:30:18,231 --> 00:30:19,463
hot men aroysgegebn

521
00:30:19,463 --> 00:30:20,649
bloye numerlekh.

522
00:30:20,757 --> 00:30:21,574
(biz s-)

